LOCUS       pH2rU3_ForInd_H5       10359 bp    DNA     circular SYN 11-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  Forward inducible lentivirus backbone coding for Delta variant 
            SARS-CoV-2 Spike (sinobiological optimization) with and 21aa CTD 
            deletion, and zsGreen that is linked to puromycin resistance gene by
            T2A linker.
ACCESSION   .
VERSION     .
KEYWORDS    .
